Available Tools: start_instance | stop_instance | restart_instance | terminate_instance
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "instance_id": "string", "region": "string" }
Response Schema: { "instance_id": "string", "state": "string", "message": "string" }
---
Question: Please start the web server instance i-a1b2c3d4 in the US East region.
Call: { "func_call": "start_instance", "instance_id": "i-a1b2c3d4", "region": "us-east-1" }
Response: { "instance_id": "i-a1b2c3d4", "state": "running", "message": "Instance i-a1b2c3d4 successfully started in us-east-1." }

Question: I need to stop the database replica i-9f8e7d6c located in Europe West.
Call: { "func_call": "stop_instance", "instance_id": "i-9f8e7d6c", "region": "eu-west-2" }
Response: { "instance_id": "i-9f8e7d6c", "state": "stopped", "message": "Instance i-9f8e7d6c successfully stopped in eu-west-2." }

Question: Can you bring up the analytics node i-55443322 in the Asia Pacific Southeast zone?
Call: { "func_call": "start_instance", "instance_id": "i-55443322", "region": "ap-southeast-1" }
Response: { "instance_id": "i-55443322", "state": "running", "message": "Instance i-55443322 successfully started in ap-southeast-1." }

